      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved specimen, offered in a condition that satisfies the most discerning collectors. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a motorcar that retains its original showroom luster, both mechanically and aesthetically. Every surface reflects meticulous stewardship, and the performance remains as precise as the day it left the factory. For those who demand nothing less than perfection, this acquisition stands as a testament to automotive excellence.",
