    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this car is. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve truly babied this ride, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been meticulously cared for and kept in top-notch shape, this is definitely the one for you. Come see it for yourself, you're going to fall in love!",
