    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with absolutely no swirls, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather is supple and free of wear, and every electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, it is flawless, backed by a complete, documented service history from authorized dealers. No accidents, no stories\u2014just a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that drives as perfectly as it looks.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
